Welcome to PH4NTXM!

PH4NTXM is a custom distribution based on Debian GNU/Linux. It brings you a stable, secure, and flexible environment, while offering a unique experience and tailored features to make your system truly your own.

The programs included with PH4NTXM are free software; the exact distribution terms for each program are described in the individual files in /usr/share/doc/*/copyright.

PH4NTXM comes with ABSOLUTELY NO WARRANTY, to the extent permitted by applicable law.
